    public interface SerializableComparator<T>
extends java.util.Comparator<T>, java.io.Serializable
    A Comparator that is also Serializable.

        static <T,V extends java.lang.Comparable<? super V>> SerializableComparator<T> comparing(SerializableFunction<? super T,? extends V> keyExtractor)
        Analogous to Comparator.comparing(Function), except that it takes in a SerializableFunction as the key extractor and returns a SerializableComparator.

        V - the type of the Comparable sort key
